function getPlugin(renderer: string) {
switch (renderer) {
case new Image().identifier():
return new Image();
case new Shape().identifier():
return new Shape();
case new Table().identifier():
return new Table();
case new Textbox().identifier():
return new Textbox();
default:
return new Raster();
}
}
